originalText.text: Danielle is an excellent teacher and loved my sessions that I took at the Plein Air Painting School.  The classes are well organized and all logistics are communicated thoroughly.  More importantly through her step by step demonstration, whether you have ever picked up a brush before or are a more experienced painter like myself, you will learn new painting techniques and walk away with a finished painting at the end of the session.  A very enjoyable way to spend a day in New York!

originalText.text: I had a fantastic experience painting with Danielle. It was my first plein air painting and I hadn't painted in oils for ages. But Danielle is an excellent teacher and I was amazed at what I could achieve in just a day.
